\par Amulet of Inescapable Location:}{\fs20\cf0  This device is typically worn on a chain or as a brooch. It appears, to magical analysis, to prevent location, scrying or detection or influence by }{\i\fs20\cf0 detect thoughts }{\fs20\cf0 
