impede movement, making him behave as if }{\i\fs20\cf0 irresistible dance }{\fs20\cf0 had been cast upon him. Only a }{\i\fs20\cf0 remove curse }{\fs20\cf0 spell enables the wearer to be rid of the boots once their true nature is revealed.
