\par }{\b\fs20\cf0 Crystal Hypnosis Ball:}{\fs20\cf0  This cursed item is indistinguishable from a normal }{\i\fs20\cf0 crystal ball. }{\fs20\cf0 However, anyone attempting to use the scrying device becomes fascinated for 1d6 minutes, and a telepathic }{
\i\fs20\cf0 suggestion }{\fs20\cf0 is implanted in his mind (Will DC 19 negates).
\par The user of the device believes that the desired creature or scene was viewed, but actually he came under the influence of a powerful wizard, lich, or even some power or being from another plane. Each further use brings the }{\i\fs20\cf0 
crystal hypnosis ball }{\fs20\cf0 gazer deeper under the influence of the controller, either as a servant or a tool. Note that throughout this time, the user remains unaware of his subjugation.
\par Moderate divination; CL 17th; In effect, this is a minor artifact and cannot be created; Price n/a.
\par }{\b\fs20\cf0 Dust of Sneezing and Choking:}{\fs20\cf0  This fine dust appears to be }{\i\fs20\cf0 dust of appearance. }{\fs20\cf0 
