immediately. In addition, those failing a second DC 15 Fortitude save 1 minute later are dealt 1d6 points of Constitution damage. Those who succeed on either saving throw are nonetheless disabled by choking (treat as stunned) for 5d4 rounds.
\par Faint conjuration; CL 7th; Create Wondrous Item, }{\i\fs20\cf0 poison; }{\fs20\cf0 Price 2,400 gp.
\par }{\b\fs20\cf0 Flask of Curses:}{\fs20\cf0  This item looks like an ordinary beaker, bottle, container, decanter, flask, or jug. It may contain a liquid, or it may emit smoke. When the flask is first unstoppered, all within 
