\par Moderate conjuration; CL 7th; Create Wondrous Item, }{\i\fs20\cf0 bestow curse; }{\fs20\cf0 Price 2,100 gp.
\par }{\b\fs20\cf0 Gauntlets of Fumbling:}{\fs20\cf0  These gauntlets may be of supple leather or heavy protective material suitable for use with armor. In the former instance, they appear to be }{\i\fs20\cf0 gloves of Dexterity. }{\fs20\cf0 
