s throat even after his death. Only when he has decayed to a dry skeleton (after approximately one month) does the necklace loosen, ready for another victim.
\par Strong conjuration; CL 18th; Create Wondrous Item, }{\i\fs20\cf0 slay living; }{\fs20\cf0 Price 60,000 gp.
