\par }{\b\fs20\cf0 The Orbs of Dragonkind:}{\fs20\cf0  Each of these fabled orbs contains the essence and personality of an ancient dragon of a different variety (one for each of the major ten different chromatic and metallic dragons). The bearer of an }{
